{ret_gewissheit1_lbl} {ret_gewissheit1} {ret_mrp_zuordnung1_lbl} {ret_mrp_zuordnung1}

Choices, Calculations, OR Slider Labels: 1, MRP bestätigt | 4, MRP bestätigt und von Stationsapotheker vorher identifiziert | 2, MRP möglich, weitere Informationen nötig | 3, MRP nicht bestätigt

select value, concat(value, ": ", 
     case (select value from [data-table] d2 where 
    project_id = [project-id] and record = [record-name] and 
    field_name = 'mrp_ip_klasse_01' and 
    (( d1.instance is null and d2.instance is null) or
     (d1.instance = d2.instance)) limit 1)
    when 1 then "Drug-Drug"
    when 2 then "Drug - Disease"
    when 3 then "Drug-Niereninsuffizienz"
    else "Keine Interpolar MRP-Klasse"
    end
    )
    from [data-table] d1
    where project_id = [project-id] and record = [record-name] and 
    field_name = 'mrp_id' and 
    value regexp concat('^(', (select group_concat(value separator '|') 
                        from [data-table] where project_id = [project-id] and 
                        record=[record-name] and field_name = 'ret_meda_id' and coalesce(instance,1) = [current-instance]), ')-') 
   order by value desc

select value, concat(value, ": ", 
     case (select value from [data-table] d2 where 
    project_id = [project-id] and record = [record-name] and 
    field_name = 'mrp_ip_klasse_01' and 
    (( d1.instance is null and d2.instance is null) or
     (d1.instance = d2.instance)) limit 1)
    when 1 then "Drug-Drug"
    when 2 then "Drug - Disease"
    when 3 then "Drug-Niereninsuffizienz"
    else "Keine Interpolar MRP-Klasse"
    end
    )
    from [data-table] d1
    where project_id = [project-id] and record = [record-name] and 
    field_name = 'mrp_id' and 
    value regexp concat('^(', (select group_concat(value separator '|') 
                        from [data-table] where project_id = [project-id] and 
                        record=[record-name] and field_name = 'ret_meda_id' and coalesce(instance,1) = [current-instance]), ')-') 
   order by value desc
